{"tid":1543780,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"除左831, 仲有9月3呢日!!!","createTime":"2019-09-05T10:14:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-05T10:35:50.000Z","uid":149829,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"635844ac063476ea4bb44f4ebe5c86435d5a50e1","tid":1543780,"uid":149829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T10:14:40.000Z","msg":"首先綜合一下, 關於831疑打死人有以下source可參考<br />\n1. 毛EE記者會蒙面女仔提及既嘔白泡人士<br />\n2. 警嫂wtsapp所講被速龍打死人士<br />\n3. 蘋果live片段入面有把女聲叫&quot;醒呀醒呀&quot;, 記者想再上前影但就俾速龍瘋狂阻止, 唔係不省人事叫人醒做乜?<br />\n4. 醫管局傳有高層證實有人死亡既wtsapp<br />\n以上既source過左咁耐都未有人證實係fake架(特別係wtsapp source), 有人死既可能性好高<br />\n<br />\n加埋太子不尋常封站, 如果咁有嫌疑啲狗都唔肯公開CCTV還自己清白, 有人死既可能就係99%<br />\n<br />\n另外大家唔好忘記9月3晚既果兩位手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n1. 帶口罩果位有哂片拍住, 中間聽到兩次嘔吐聲, 黑警唔俾FA去救, 好似冇哂反應, 最後仲要拖行佢走, 不知去向 (有老豆話佢清醒係呢位?)<br />\n2. 送院果位(著住校服?) 睇圖似係頸傷(咁呢位最後咩情況?)<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BBVP1Ep.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBBVP1Ep.jpg&h=3c24bf72&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Px9Utjr.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPx9Utjr.png&h=b72c1d74&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n呢兩幅圖唔會係同一個??<br />\n<br />\n831已經懷疑死左一個, 9月3果個又係不省人事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">一定要追究到底!!!</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"1c14d18d16f72793c19272331b282a0aba25920c","tid":1543780,"uid":149829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T10:17:23.000Z","msg":"1"},{"pid":"b1b48ad876e924943e9949532534580e74b75f85","tid":1543780,"uid":149829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T10:17:52.000Z","msg":"2"},{"pid":"d839b1d3088c927620395294643565bcf92f1bb3","tid":1543780,"uid":683